# Cantrips


# Spellbooks
spellbook-spellbook-blink-name = Blink Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-blink-description = Don't blink or you'll miss yourself teleporting away.

spellbook-spellbook-fireball-name = Fireball Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-fireball-description = Get most crew exploding with rage when they see this fireball heading toward them!

spellbook-spellbook-force-wall-name = Force Wall Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-force-wall-description = Make three walls of pure force that you can pass through, but others can't.

spellbook-spellbook-knock-name = Knock Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-knock-description = Opens all airlocks, crates and lockers nearby.

spellbook-spellbook-smite-name = Smite Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-smite-description = Don't like them? EXPLODE them into giblets!

spellbook-spellbook-spawn-name = Spawn Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-spawn-description = Conjure forth three magicarp, to your aid or to your detriment!


